number of cross overs per chromosome 4 - arabidopsis

Load libraries and the data

Arabidopsis recombination landscape data is published in the following manuscript
http://www.nature.com/hdy/journal/v108/n4/full/hdy201195a.html.

Supplemental information from above manuscript is downloaded and is in the following folder recombination_landscape
